title: How to Enhance Your Home's Interior

steps.headline: Find a style.
steps.description: The first step toward enhancing your home should be to determine the style that most reflects your personality (Ex. Outdoorsy, Classic, Modern, etc.)

steps.headline: Collect items.
steps.description: Once this style is determined, begin to collect art, knick knacks, fabrics, and textures that display your interests.

steps.headline: Experiment with various placements of these objects to see what appeals to you the most and what will "Draw in" your visitors (Ex.
steps.description: Try moving lamps to different locations to showcase various lighting, or place throws on various pieces of furniture to add warmth and texture to your room.)

text: Find a style. The first step toward enhancing your home should be to determine the style that most reflects your personality (Ex. Outdoorsy, Classic, Modern, etc.) Collect items. Once this style is determined, begin to collect art, knick knacks, fabrics, and textures that display your interests. Experiment with various placements of these objects to see what appeals to you the most and what will "Draw in" your visitors (Ex. Try moving lamps to different locations to showcase various lighting, or place throws on various pieces of furniture to add warmth and texture to your room.)
